<TEXT>
   One of a set of quintuplets born three months
prematurely has died of complications caused by the early birth, a
hospital spokeswoman said Saturday.
   Rachel Lauren Simunich died Friday afternoon at Magee-Womens
Hospital, said spokeswoman Mary Hughes.
   The parents, Terry Simunich, 26, and her husband, Max, 28, of
