   Bradley Andrew came first, followed by Emily Marie, Allison
Nicole, Rachel and Kathryn Elizabeth. The girls ranged from 1 pound
8 ounces to 1 pound 10 ounces.
   The couple asked the hospital to withhold details concerning the
infant's death, Ms. Hughes said.
