<HEAD>Robert Redford Arrives In Soviet Union</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Actor Robert Redford arrived in the Soviet Union
on Saturday for a 10-day tour to attend showings of his films and
meet film audiences in three cities, Tass said.
   Redford arrived in Leningrad, where the city's largest movie
theater was showing a selection of his films including ``All the
